Cell.Text: Are you Fjol?
Yes. I'm. I believe you are the recruit, I'm right?
Yes, I'm. We found the Wuuthrad fragment on Angarvunde's treasure.

Is that true? Brave! We are one piece closer to finishing that puzzle! | As Krev may have told you, we the Silver Hand have been searching for the pieces of Wuuthrad for some centuries now. | It was broken into twelve pieces hundreds of years ago. Right now, the Dogs in Whiterun have four pieces. | But, thanks to your help, we new have five fragments.

Node.Caption: DSilHand_M30_FMTopic02: Yes, I'm. We found the Wuuthrad fragment on Angarvunde's treasure.

Cell.Text: Dogs in Whiterun?
Yes. The Companions. The members of the circle. They are werewolves. All of them.
Members of the Circle?
Their leaders. They say they are all equals. That was true in the past. Centuries ago. | Before they started to worship Hircine. Now, all the members of the circle share the same beast blood.
How do you know that?

This is a long history. Let's I and Krev were invited to become beasts, and refused the "gift". | But we didn't want to stay quiet as well. Now, they are persecuting us. | Enough talk about the past... Soon we may talk more about that. Now I need a favor. | Could you please talk to an informant we have on Winterhold? He is called Nelacar. | Just ask him if he still has that silver ring to sell. If he has any good news, he will find a way to tell you.
Consider the task done!
[S] Good Brother! That's the spirit! Please, be discrete as possible. No one should know he is our informant.
Do you still have that silver ring to sell?

Node.Caption: DSilHand_M30_WITopic01: Do you still have that silver ring to sell?

Cell.Text: I found another fragment. The mages were studying it.
[S] I can't believe it. Ysgramor must be helping us from Sovngarde, somehow!

Node.Caption: DSilHand_M30_FFLTopic01: I found another fragment. The mages were studying it.

Cell.Text: Also, Nelacar has given to me this letter.

Let me see... | That is amazing! The mages of the college have discovered another possible location for the next fragment! | Dustman's Cairn... I know where this place is. | The letter says they were going to inform the Companions about the location... | We must hurry! We must go fast and be there as soon as possible. | I'll mark the location on your map. I'll make the arrangements and gather some manpower for the excavations. | Meet me there in a few hours, we must be there before the Companions!

Node.Caption: DSilHand_M30_FFLTopic02: Also, Nelacar has given to me this letter.

Cell.Text: I'll be there!

[S] Good! Before we continue, I need to thank you for your efforts so far. | Take this sword as a reward. It is a silver sword, but with a secret tempering method that uses dwemer oil. | This tempering makes it as hard and sharp as ebony. | Talk with Kurdak if you want to learn more about this process.
